Module gamecritic
Package profile_strategy

Interface ProfileStrategyInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
AdministratorStrategy, CriticStrategy, UserStrategy
public interface ProfileStrategyInterface
Defines the strategy interface for configuring gui components based on the users role. This strategy pattern allows for dynamic changes in the user interface of a profile, adapting it to different user types.

    • setInterface

      void setInterface(javafx.scene.control.Label balanceValueLabel, javafx.scene.control.Label additionalTextLabel, javafx.scene.shape.Line additionalLine, javafx.scene.control.Button generateAwardsButton, javafx.scene.control.Button transferFundsButton, javafx.scene.control.Button addNewGameButton)
      Sets the interface elements specific to users profile strategy. This method configures labels, lines, and buttons according to the needs of different user roles.
      Parameters:
      balanceValueLabel - label to display balance information
      additionalTextLabel - label for displaying additional text related to user role
      additionalLine - line that separate sections
      generateAwardsButton - button for triggering awards generation for administrator
      transferFundsButton - button for initiating funds transfer for critic
      addNewGameButton - button for adding new games for administrator
